# Root-context builds (claude-code, pa-worker, email-poller, gdrive-poller)
# send the stack dir as context — keep it lean. checker-mcp/outlook-mcp build
# from their own subdirs and are unaffected by this file.
**/node_modules
**/.venv
**/__pycache__
**/*.pyc
**/*.db
**/*.db-wal
**/*.db-shm
**/.pytest_cache
.git/
.github/
.env
.env.*
config/
data/
docs/
tests/
checker-mcp/
outlook-mcp/
_tasks/
